							    • Name of Race: This is the official name of the event he will be competing in. 
							  <br>
							    • Date of Race: It’s the date of the Race event. 
							  <br>
							    • Price Per Mile: The amount of money that the athletes prices his miles.
							   <br>
							    • NonProfit Organization: The name of the  Non Profit that will receive all the money from the Challenge.
