							  <br>
							    • Stripe collects the money charged to donors and transfers that money to the nonprofit organizations directly. No money is transferred to MyMiles.  Stripe currently pays the Non Profits in seven days, and in some cases may be lower. (see Stripe’s Terms and Conditions)
